title: S3 E4 Best Rangers 2022 -  CPT Josh Corson and CPT Ty Boyle
description:
Winners of the 2022 Best Ranger Competition, from the 75th Ranger Regiment CPT Joshua Corson and CPT Tymothy Boyle join the hosts of SOFcast to talk about what it took to not only complete the three-day grueling event but to beat 50 other teams. Tenacity, endurance, and faith, these Rangers indeed lead the way!

Subscribe to SOFcast today!
